<p>
<note n="0928005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0928005">〔俱舍論頌疏〕－【甲】</note>
<note n="0928006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0928006">此下乙本有中大雲寺沙門圓暉述，分別隨眠品第五之二十八字</note>
<note n="0929001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0929001">〔而〕－【甲】</note>
<note n="0929002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0929002">又＝文【甲】</note>
<note n="0930001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0930001">起＝也【甲】</note>
